{
  "title": "Creamy Smoky Greek Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A rich and smoky Greek lamb stew with a velvety texture, served with crumbled muffins, this solo dinner dish is a hearty and comforting meal.",
  "cuisine": "Greek",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
    "raw-friendly"
